OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FFugitive aristocrat Constance Marten
OL,7,Fwas advised by her partner to say
OL,8,Ftheir baby was the victim of "cot
OL,9,Fdeath", after the child died in her
OL,10,Farms as she slept, a court has heard.
OL,12,FMarten, 36, and Mark Gordon, 49,
OL,13,Fdisappeared and went on the run with
OL,14,Ftheir daughter Victoria after their
OL,15,Fcar burst into flames near Bolton,
OL,16,FGreater Manchester, in January 2023.
OL,18,FThe couple went on to sleep in a tent,
OL,19,Fin a bid to keep the baby, after
OL,20,FMarten's four other children were
OL,21,Ftaken into care, the Old Bailey heard.
