OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FWhen the couple were eventually
OL,7,Farrested in Brighton, East Sussex,
OL,8,Fthey initially refused to say where
OL,9,Ftheir child was or whether she was
OL,10,Falive or dead.
OL,12,FOn 1 March last year, Victoria's
OL,13,Fremains were found in a Lidl
OL,14,Fsupermarket bag inside a disused shed
OL,15,Fon an allotment.
OL,17,FIn the following police interviews,
OL,18,FMarten gave an account of how Victoria
OL,19,Fhad died six or seven days after the
OL,20,Fcar fire.
