OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FShe told police she had been
OL,7,F"extremely tired" and had fallen
OL,8,Fasleep in a tent while holding
OL,9,FVictoria under her jacket.
OL,11,FWhen she woke up, Victoria had gone
OL,12,F"limp" and did not respond to
OL,13,Fresuscitation attempts, the defendant
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FMarten said she did not seek help
OL,17,Fbecause the child was no longer alive.
OL,19,FShe said she wrapped the baby up and
OL,20,Fheld her for hours before putting her
OL,21,Fin a bag.
