OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FShe said: "Initially Mark and I were
OL,7,Ftalking about what to do with the
OL,8,Fsituation and I think, like two weeks
OL,9,Fafter it happened, I was debating
OL,10,Fwhether to hand myself in.
OL,12,F"Mark advised me to say it was a cot
OL,13,Fdeath and I was not holding her.
OL,15,F"And he advised me to say that I lay
OL,16,Fher down and then when we woke up she
OL,17,Fwas on her front and she's passed away.
