OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,F"But that isn't what happened. So he
OL,7,Fmay try to say that in order to
OL,8,Fprotect me because he wants to protect
OL,9,Fmy interests."
OL,11,FMarten told police she and Gordon were
OL,12,Fboth "distraught" when Victoria died.
OL,14,FShe said she felt "shock, sadness,
OL,15,Fgrief and anger" that they had done so
OL,16,Fmuch to keep her and it "ended really
OL,17,Fbadly".
