OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FThe defendant said she left the bag
OL,7,Fcontaining Victoria's body at the
OL,8,Fallotment when it became too heavy to
OL,9,Fcarry.
OL,11,FShe covered the child's body in soil
OL,12,Fbecause of the smell, jurors heard.
OL,14,FMarten told police she had planned to
OL,15,Fbury Victoria's body and considered
OL,16,Fcremating her, but changed her mind.
OL,18,FThe defendant said that before the
OL,19,Ftragedy she had been "elated" to be
OL,20,Fwith one of her children.
