OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FShe said: "I was feeling fine. I was
OL,7,Felated to be with her actually. To be
OL,8,Fwith one of my children. With Mark,
OL,9,Ftogether and parenting."
OL,11,FThey had not intended to stay in a
OL,12,Ftent for long and the baby had warm
OL,13,Fblankets and clothes, she said.
OL,15,FBut Marten told officers that they
OL,16,Ffound themselves "between a rock and a
OL,17,Fhard place".
OL,19,F"We had limited cash. I knew that I
OL,20,Fcouldn't access the bank because then
OL,21,Fthe police would know where I was."
