OL,3,CConstance Marten told to say baby was
OL,4,Cvictim of 'cot death', jury told
OL,6,FShe added: "We were trying to figure
OL,7,Fout what to do in terms of getting a
OL,8,Fhouse, accessing money without the
OL,9,Fauthorities finding out where we were."
OL,11,FMarten and Gordon, of no fixed
OL,12,Faddress, deny manslaughter, perverting
OL,13,Fthe course of justice, concealing the
OL,14,Fbirth of a child, child cruelty and
OL,15,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,16,Fchild.
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
